"tool to compare a series of land productivity maps generated using EO data "
"but varying algorithmic approaches. During a participatory workshop, "
"participants examined the various maps and by pooling their expert knowledge"
" and the outcomes of the analysis, they were able to choose a map which "
"aligned most closely with the known situation in the country. This example "
"is described in more detail in [The Land "
"Story](https://www.unccd.int/resources/publications/land-story-country-"
