msgid ""
"Degradation hotspots (for countries that provide spatial data in the PRAIS 4"
" platform)"
msgstr ""
"Les zones sensibles à la dégradation (pour les pays qui fournissent des "
"données spatiales sur la plateforme du système PRAIS 4) ;"

#: ../../SO1.md:1449
msgid ""
"Improvement brightspots (for countries that provide spatial data in the "
