"The default UNCCD land cover legend for aggregate reporting is a modified "
"version of the Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change land use "
"categories, where ‘water bodies’ are separated from ‘wetlands’ and grouped "
"in a seventh class including: lakes, rivers and streams (natural/artificial,"
" standing/flowing, inland/sea), artificial reservoirs, coastal lagoons, and "
"estuaries."
